— from the precision-machined housing to the retractable cable system.</p>\n  <div class=\"gz-features-grid\">\n    <div class=\"gz-feature\">\n      <svg class=\"gz-feature-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"/></svg>\n      <h3 class=\"gz-feature-title\">PD Fast Charging</h3>\n      <p class=\"gz-feature-body\">Power Delivery via USB-C — charges your phone from 0 to 50% in about 25 minutes. Compatible with the latest iPhone and Android.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gz-feature\">\n      <svg class=\"gz-feature-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M6 12h.01M10 12h.01M14 12h.01M18 12h.01\"/></svg>\n      <h3 class=\"gz-feature-title\">Four Devices, One Charger</h3>\n      <p class=\"gz-feature-body\">USB-C plus dual USB-A plus a built-in retractable cable — power your phone, tablet, dashcam, and a passenger's device simultaneously.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gz-feature\">\n      <svg class=\"gz-feature-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"18\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/><line x1=\"7\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"10\"/><line x1=\"13\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"17\" y2=\"10\"/><line x1=\"7\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"17\" y2=\"14\"/></svg>\n      <h3 class=\"gz-feature-title\">Digital Voltage Display</h3>\n      <p class=\"gz-feature-body\">Real-time readout on the integrated screen lets you monitor charging at a glance — no guesswork, no surprise drainage.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gz-feature\">\n      <svg class=\"gz-feature-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/></svg>\n      <h3 class=\"gz-feature-title\">Premium Metal Build</h3>\n      <p class=\"gz-feature-body\">Precision-machined aluminum housing. Retractable cable that stays clean. 180° adjustable angle that fits any car interior.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
